{"tid":1116842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃心穎事業一鋪清？樂易玲：換其他藝人取代","createTime":"2019-04-20T09:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T08:19:54.000Z","uid":82845,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8fb3bc76815f170f2011ec4370a65da6a6d578","tid":1116842,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"無綫高層樂易玲今晚到紅館欣賞吳業坤演唱會，期間被問到旗下女藝人黃心穎於偷食事件中形象盡毁，致所有工作及劇集都要抽起？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她說：「坦白講，係嘅！Job、商演、出埠嘅工作，都換咗其他藝人取代！（賠償？）啲客好好，冇要求賠償，（劇集要入雪櫃？）希望時間快啲過啦！（解約？）暫未諗呢個問題，因為仲有好長約，停一陣先，呢個都係佢意願，因為佢都做唔到嘢！（安排佢出嚟交代？）等佢Ready後就可以！（心情未平復？）一時時啦，尋日有聯絡佢，知佢情緒唔係好穩定，成日喊！（佢依家喺邊？）佢喺香港！（怕佢做傻事？）有佢家姐上佢屋企睇住！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於另一位受害人馬國明，仍繼續開工，樂易玲大讚他專業：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>係絕世好男人，好Man﹑好靚仔！</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190419/bkn-20190419210226468-0419_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190419%2Fbkn-20190419210226468-0419_00862_001.html&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=3dea8ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190419/bkn-20190419210226468-0419_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b2581c36c296dd1c92c1852a8d3ec354bc378b9b","tid":1116842,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"奀星 WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb2f38154f8eccf83fef5c33baf478ec6c6af9e","tid":1116842,"uid":3467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"正臭閪<br />\n咪撚出黎獻世<br />\n無人想睇佢"},{"pid":"49d5040396098dfdd9108403adfd2d373678469f","tid":1116842,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0